Text:
I forgot to include the compatibility patch for DH version 1.02.

Get that one here:
http://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/showthread.php?556921-Mod-33-for-Darkest-Hour-is-released&p=13080826&viewfull=1#post13080826

This torrent version only works with 2.01, if you have the current DH version which is 2.02, you need above patch! Just extract it to the Mod33 folder after you installed the main mod.
